OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,FA doctor who was stabbed by a fellow
OL,7,Fplastic surgeon thought an intruder
OL,8,Fwas his son in an attempt to
OL,9,F"rationalise" the situation before he
OL,10,Fwas attacked, a court has heard.
OL,12,FJurors were told Graeme Perks was
OL,13,Fblinded by the head torch of a man he
OL,14,Fthought was wearing a balaclava before
OL,15,Fbeing stabbed in the abdomen, leaving
OL,16,Fhim in intensive care.
