OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,FLoughborough Courthouse heard Peter
OL,7,FBrooks, a specialist in plastics and
OL,8,Fburns, attempted to murder Mr Perks
OL,9,Fwhile armed with a crowbar, petrol,
OL,10,Fmatches and a knife after cycling to
OL,11,Fhis home in Halam, Nottinghamshire in
OL,12,Fthe early hours of January 14 2021.
OL,14,FProsecutors said the 61-year-old
OL,15,Fdoused the ground floor of the
OL,16,Fproperty in petrol before stabbing Mr
OL,17,FPerks, who he "hated" because he was
OL,18,Fgiving evidence in a work disciplinary
OL,19,Fhearing against the defendant.
