OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,FMr Perks, who was aged 65 at the time
OL,7,Fof the attack, had only recently
OL,8,Fretired, the court heard.
OL,10,FPolice gave evidence of a video
OL,11,Finterview which was recorded with them
OL,12,Feight days after Mr Perks was
OL,13,Fdischarged from hospital.
OL,15,FThe footage shows the father-of-four
OL,16,Fwho said he went to bed on the night
OL,17,Fof the attack between 10pm and 11:30pm
OL,18,Fand lived with his wife and youngest
OL,19,Fson.
