OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,FHe told detectives: "At some unknown
OL,7,Ftime I heard a loud noise, it was
OL,8,Fsufficient to wake me. It was really
OL,9,Funusual.
OL,11,F"When I heard that bang I thought
OL,12,Fsomething seriously wrong was
OL,13,Fhappening in the house. We live in a
OL,14,Fplace that's really quiet.
OL,16,F"To hear a noise like that signified
OL,17,Fsomething serious was going on.
OL,19,F"It was a loud bang. I thought,
OL,20,F'somebody's trying to break in'.
