OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,F"I simply leapt out of bed. Didn't
OL,7,Fwaste time looking at the clock. I am
OL,8,Fa fairly light sleeper ` if I do hear
OL,9,Fsomething it will wake me up.
OL,11,F"I recall jumping out of bed ` I sleep
OL,12,Fnaked ` and I recall running down the
OL,13,Fstairs into the drawing room and my
OL,14,Frecollection was there appeared to be
OL,15,Fa huge hole in the left hand door of
OL,16,Fthe conservatory.
