OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,F"I thought I smelt something unusual
OL,7,Fbut wasn't really with it. I vaguely
OL,8,Frecall my feet being damp. I saw a
OL,9,Ffigure in the garden wearing dark
OL,10,Fclothing with their back to me.
OL,12,F"Mr Perks thought the figure was his
OL,13,Fson because he had the same "big,
OL,14,Fsolid" build, and in his confusion
OL,15,Fthought his son was "having a mental
OL,16,Fbreakdown".
