OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,FHe said: "I have no reason for him to
OL,7,Fdo that because he has been perfectly
OL,8,Fnormal for 29 years ` my brain was
OL,9,Ftrying to rationalise it."
OL,11,FMr Perks told detectives he said "what
OL,12,Fthe hell is going on?" to the figure,
OL,13,Fwho turned around, but the victim
OL,14,Fcould not see their face because they
OL,15,Fhad a headlight on and he thought they
OL,16,Fmight be wearing a balaclava.
OL,18,F"Nothing was said, and the next thing
OL,19,FI remember was feeling a blow to my
OL,20,Fbody.
