OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,F"I put my hands to the area where I
OL,7,Ffelt it and it was warm and sticky,
OL,8,Fand I thought I felt something poking
OL,9,Fout from my abdomen and I decided that
OL,10,FI must have been stabbed, and that I
OL,11,Fneeded to get back to the house.
OL,13,F"I turned back towards the house then
OL,14,FI don't remember anything that
OL,15,Fhappened after that."I was totally
OL,16,Fconfused as to what was going on.
OL,17,FNothing was said.
