OL,3,C'I thought the intruder was my son',
OL,4,Cdoctor stabbed by surgeon tells court
OL,6,F"I don't remember it being painful at
OL,7,Fall, I just remember it was a blow. My
OL,8,Flast recollection is just turning back
OL,9,Fto the house. I have no recollection
OL,10,Fof where I ended up at all."
OL,12,FMr Perks said he was in intensive care
OL,13,Ffor eight days and in hospital the
OL,14,Ffollowing three weeks, during which he
OL,15,Fhad "hallucinations" and said "some of
OL,16,Fit must come from the recollection of
OL,17,Fthe smell of petrol" but also he had
OL,18,Fbeen given lots of drugs, the court
OL,19,Fheard.
